data.description: *** PRICE REDUCTION AND SELLER WILL PAY UP TO $5000 TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS*** Rare opportunity to own this custom-built townhome in the coveted White Barn Golf Community is situated on one of the golf courses largest ponds with amazing views of the tree lined course and mountains. It boasts beautiful, generously sized rooms flooded with natural light from the large windows and skylights, creating an inviting and warm atmosphere throughout. Located in a fantastic maintenance free neighborhood, this property offers the perfect blend of convenience and comfort. Everything you need all on the ground floor with a spacious kitchen, vaulted ceilings, and plenty of extra space upstairs. Take advantage of the all the storage with copious closets and shelves throughout the interior and attic access above the attached two-car garage.  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
